hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted mediks24.gq This is all part of meeting Polman’s target to help a billion people – one in seven of the planet’s population – to improve their personal hygiene by 2020. So far it claims to have influenced 224 million. But for all its snooping, some changes are proving hard, the bathroom boffins admit. Even though the company has come up with ways for us to rinse our hair quicker in the shower, its trackers reveal that we still spend the same amount of time in there. 'We are starting to wonder what people do in there,’ Wright said. He’ll find out soon enough.
